Spinister looked up to his leaving enemy, then let Singe transform. He
then transformed into his helicopter mode, and Singe got in, as he
followed Havotron back to base.


Hook tried to pull himself up, but was no longer able to, and his eyes
went off line, as he fell back to the ground motionless.
